title: [Kwagmire Kourt, Outer Rim]
description: Wooden planks that long ago warped into bent and twisted shapes are all that allow passage into this dank, muck-filled grotto.  A few trees solemnly greet visitors to the area, their trunks deeply submerged within the swamp, and their long, thick leaves bending down so far as to brush the brackish water.

Wooden planks that long ago warped into bent and twisted shapes are all that allow passage into this dank, muck-filled grotto.  A few trees solemnly greet visitors to the area, their trunks deeply submerged within the swamp, and their long, thick leaves bending down so far as to brush the brackish water.  A pair of guttering torches cast a fitful light against the almost tangible gloom.
